Persian word list (curated mini-dictionary)
============================================

This file is a small bundled dictionary used by:

  * `normalize_persian(text, use_dictionary=True)` — for dictionary-aware
    repeated-letter collapse (preserves legitimate doubles like الله, موسسه,
    تردد, محقق).
  * `spellcheck(text)` — for finding the closest dictionary word within
    edit distance 1.

For production use, replace this file with the full 453K-word list from
https://github.com/shahind/Persian-Words-Database (the dictionary davat
uses) — the API is the same: one word per line, UTF-8.

The words below were curated to cover:
  - Common verbs (past/present stems, infinitives)
  - High-frequency nouns and adjectives
  - Words with legitimate doubled letters (للله, سس, دد, حقق, etc.)
  - Common prefixes/suffixes as standalone words

Lines starting with `#` are comments and are skipped.
